It may be distributed by disk, as long as no more than 1 UKP is charged
for the disk.
It may be distributed on a CD, as long as no more than 20 UKP is
charged for the CD.
@endnode

@node Features
@next Installation
@prev Introduction
* Small:
  UMS-QWK's importer was 14k, and it's exporter 13k.
  PR-QWK is 20k, making it 7k smaller than UMS-QWK.

* Fast:
  UMS-QWK imports at approx. 11 messages/second.
  PR-QWK imports at approx. 13 messages/second.

  @{"Test Results" link TestResults}
@endnode

